title: Galaxy Wars Defense v1.8.3 Final bobiras2009
description:
This is a Space Sci-Fi Defense Game with Stunning Graphics and Super Big Maps!
Galaxy Wars is the most anticipated and visually stunning Defense game.
If you don't get free reward points, please open free version and click the item again.

Please aware the record files are in folder 'sdcard/catstudio/', if you want change or reset your SD card please backup this folder #
please turn off sound on SamSung Galaxy S2(I9100) to avoid force closes(if you have this issue)

Features:

    Stunning Graphics, Particle Effects and Animations.
    Super big maps with the resolution of 1380x900 and 1980x1200! HD graphics especially for pad.
    12 maps with three levels of difficulty(coming more).
    Interactive terrain with open path.
    8 Types of Towers with 3 Upgrade Levels Each.
    3 game modes: Classic, Extended & Endless.
    Pinch zoom in/out battle field.
    Weapons shop and achievements make game more interesting to play a long time.

What's in this version : (Updated : Aug 1, 2012)

    Fix some display bugs.
    Your 5 star rating keeps us motivated to produce upcoming updates to make Galaxy Wars even better!

Required Android O/S : 1.6+
